genresAdvancedInfo.name: viet remix
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Viet remix is a genre of music that originated in Vietnam and is a fusion of traditional Vietnamese music with modern electronic dance music. It features remixes of popular Vietnamese songs and incorporates elements of EDM, house, and trance. The genre is popular in clubs and at parties and has gained a following across Southeast Asia.
